                              <p style="margin-bottom: 1em;">John Goodman, Aldona Robbins, and Gary Robbins, “Elderly Taxpayers and the Capital Gains Tax Debate,” National Center for Policy Analysis, Dallas, Texas, 1990.</p>
                            </span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <!--endofchap-->
